# Healthcare Analytics

## Project Overview
This project analyzes healthcare patient data and predicts medical test results using Machine Learning techniques.

## Tools Used
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn
- Scikit-learn
- Streamlit

## Project Workflow

1. Data Loading
- Loaded healthcare dataset
- Checked data structure and information

2. Data Cleaning
- Handled missing values
- Removed unnecessary columns
- Prepared dataset for modeling

3. Exploratory Data Analysis
- Analyzed patient demographics
- Visualized medical conditions
- Created correlation analysis

4. Feature Engineering
- Converted categorical variables using Label Encoding
- Prepared features for Machine Learning model

5. Machine Learning Model
- Built classification model
- Evaluated model performance
- Saved trained model

6. Streamlit Application
- Created interactive web application
- User can enter patient details and get prediction results

